reviews.review_text: concerning St.Stephen I must say that this is the worst version I've ever heard of St. Stephen. It doesn't even go into the slow part about lady fingers dipped in moonlight. Pretty lame, I must say. I've heard and expect so much better from the dead. They must have eaten too much L that show.
that guy is retarded this St. Stephen does indeed go into the lady fingers part, idk what your're talking about man. sound quality isn't too good, but its cool to hear the audience getting into it
